<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><fdroid><repo icon="icon.png" name="funkypitt's F-Droid Repo" pubkey="" timestamp="1777320590" url="https://funkypitt.github.io/fdroid-repo/repo" version="20002"><description>Personal F-Droid repository with custom apps: Pluralis (alternative news aggregator) and OpenLibe Extended (e-ink library client).</description></repo><application id="com.local2p.games"><id>com.local2p.games</id><added>2026-04-01</added><lastupdated>2026-04-27</lastupdated><name>2P Games</name><summary>16 multiplayer games — play locally or online. No ads, no accounts.</summary><desc>2P Games is a collection of 16 touch-friendly multiplayer games for two
players. Play locally on one device or online with a friend. No accounts,
no ads.

10 games support online play via room codes or quick match:
4 in a Row, Caro, Awalé, Memory, Bulls &amp; Cows, Tank Wars, Ship Battle,
Dots &amp; Boxes, Word Clash, and Tic Tac Toe.

Also includes Tennis (with power-ups), Pool, Word Clash, Air Hockey, Mini Golf,
Star Clash, Wheel of Funktune, and Horse Jump.

Each game has built-in instructions accessible via the ? button.

All games feature intuitive touch controls. Built-in calming background
music with toggle. Every game has rematch support.

Free and open source. No ads. No tracking. No in-app purchases.
